        <akn:num>16-831.08</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Factors to consider in determining best interests of child.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_16-831_08_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>In determining whether custody with a third party, pursuant to this chapter, is in the childâ€™s best interests, the court shall consider all relevant factors, including:</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_16-831_08_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>There shall be a rebuttable presumption that granting custody to a third party who has committed an intrafamily offense is not in the best interest of the child.</akn:p></akn:content>
